The Prince Of Peace: The Christmas Story | Full Movie 

The birth of baby Jesus in a Bethlehem stable changed the world. See the story unfold in captivating 3D animation as angels visit Mary and Joseph while Herod plots to erase any competition to his throne. 

Meet the innkeeper and his wife, who protect the baby, while shepherds come to worship the One called by many today "The Prince of Peace."
